- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of RGB-D scans for robot navigation and manipulation tasks.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes a new neural network architecture for 3D scene completion.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is possible as the paper deals with generating 3D surfaces and scenes.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper proposes a self-supervised approach for 3D scene completion.
